                            ],
                            Label: "leave_button"
                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "You are standing in an active yield zone. The family that mismanaged this parcel has been transitioned to alternative outcomes, and the parcel now performs. Look at it. Rows. Numbers. Performance."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "I run six fields like this one off a single clipboard. This one is my favorite, because it was first. Everything the Company plans to do, it practiced here."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Manager — the quota",
                    Label: "quota"
                },
